sive empirical evaluation on several large, real-life graphs\ndemonstrates effectiveness and scalability of the proposed methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Aug 2016 03:57:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2017 07:25:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 29 Apr 2018 04:57:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-01"}
